Release: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/rust-analyzer/rust-analyzer/releases/2024-11-18&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;2024-11-18&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;code&gt;v0.3.2188&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
